Detailed Description

cvmx_mix::_ircnt

MIX_IRCNT = MIX I-Ring Pending Packet Counter

Description: NOTE: To write to the MIX_IRCNT register, a device would issue an IOBST directed at the MIO. To read the MIX_IRCNT register, a device would issue an IOBLD64 directed at the MIO.
